  <p class="ex-para ex-saturn-body">Themes, templates, UI kits, and digital assets built for other designers and developers. Products that encode the same standards I hold in client work. Placeholder — update with your actual product catalogue.</p>
  <div class="ex-saturn-stats-row">
    <div class="ex-saturn-stat-pill"><span class="ex-saturn-stat-pill-value">[N] products</span><span class="ex-saturn-stat-pill-label">Available</span></div>
    <div class="ex-saturn-stat-pill"><span class="ex-saturn-stat-pill-value">[Platform]</span><span class="ex-saturn-stat-pill-label">Where to buy</span></div>
  </div>
  <button class="ex-saturn-intro-cta" type="button" data-scroll-next>
    BROWSE PRODUCTS
